<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>مفاصل | العرض التقديمي</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tajawal:wght@300;400;500;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
  <link rel="icon" href="/icons/logo.png">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    :root {
      --accent: #12a99b;
      --accent2: #0d8a7e;
      --primary: #101d23;
      --primary-light: #1a2e38;
      --text: #e8ecf0;
      --text-muted: #8899a6;
      --gold: #f5c542;
      --blue: #3b82f6;
      --purple: #8b5cf6;
      --pink: #ec4899;
      --red: #ef4444;
      --green: #22c55e;
      --orange: #f59e0b;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; scroll-snap-type: y mandatory; overflow-y: scroll; overflow-x: hidden; }
    body { font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif; background: var(--primary); color: var(--text); }

    .slide {
      min-height: 100vh;
      min-height: 100dvh;
      scroll-snap-align: start;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .slide-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      width: 100%;
      z-index: 2;
      position: relative;
    }

    .bg-glow {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      filter: blur(120px);
      opacity: 0.15;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .slide-num {
      position: absolute;
      top: 2rem;
      left: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      opacity: 0.5;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }
    .badge-accent { background: rgba(18,169,155,0.15); color: var(--accent); border: 1px solid rgba(18,169,155,0.25); }
    .badge-blue { background: rgba(59,130,246,0.12); color: var(--blue); border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.2); }
    .badge-purple { background: rgba(139,92,246,0.12); color: var(--purple); border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.2); }
    .badge-gold { background: rgba(245,197,66,0.12); color: var(--gold); border: 1px solid rgba(245,197,66,0.2); }
    .badge-pink { background: rgba(236,72,153,0.12); color: var(--pink); border: 1px solid rgba(236,72,153,0.2); }
    .badge-green { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.12); color: var(--green); border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.2); }
    .badge-orange { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.12); color: var(--orange); border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.2); }
    .badge-red { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.12); color: var(--red); border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.2); }

    h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.25; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    h2 { font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.4rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .subtitle { font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.2rem); color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.8; max-width: 700px; }
    .accent { color: var(--accent); }
    .blue { color: var(--blue); }
    .purple { color: var(--purple); }
    .gold { color: var(--gold); }
    .pink { color: var(--pink); }
    .green { color: var(--green); }

    .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.25rem; }
    .grid-4 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1rem; }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      transition: transform 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: rgba(18,169,155,0.3); }

    .card-icon {
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .card p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; }

    .mockup-phone {
      width: 260px;
      height: 520px;
      background: var(--primary-light);
      border-radius: 36px;
      border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
      position: relative;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .mockup-phone::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 12px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 80px;
      height: 24px;
      background: var(--primary);
      border-radius: 12px;
      z-index: 5;
    }
    .mockup-screen {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 2.5rem 1rem 1rem;
    }
    .mockup-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .mockup-header img { width: 24px; height: 24px; }
    .mockup-header span { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .mockup-item {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 0.65rem 0.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
    }
    .mockup-item-icon {
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .mockup-btn {
      margin-top: auto;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 0.7rem;
      font-family: inherit;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .stat-big {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }
    .stat-big-num {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .stat-big-label {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-top: 0.3rem;
    }

    .timeline {
      position: relative;
      padding-right: 2rem;
    }
    .timeline::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      right: 0;
      top: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent), var(--purple), var(--blue));
      border-radius: 2px;
    }
    .timeline-item {
      position: relative;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem 1.5rem 0;
    }
    .timeline-item::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      right: -0.45rem;
      top: 1.3rem;
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 3px solid var(--accent);
      background: var(--primary);
    }
    .timeline-item:nth-child(2)::before { border-color: var(--purple); }
    .timeline-item:nth-child(3)::before { border-color: var(--blue); }
    .timeline-item:nth-child(4)::before { border-color: var(--gold); }

    .tech-stack {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.6rem;
    }
    .tech-tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .tech-tag:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }

    .nav-dots {
      position: fixed;
      left: 1.5rem;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      z-index: 100;
    }
    .nav-dot {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      border: none;
    }
    .nav-dot.active { background: var(--accent); height: 24px; border-radius: 5px; }
    .nav-dot:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }

    .top-bar {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
      background: rgba(16,29,35,0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }
    .top-bar-brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .top-bar-brand img { width: 28px; height: 28px; }
    .top-bar-brand span { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .top-bar-links { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; }
    .top-bar-links a {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .top-bar-links a:hover { color: var(--text); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
    .top-bar-links .cta {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
    }
    .top-bar-links .cta:hover { background: var(--accent2); }

    .divider-line {
      width: 60px;
      height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), transparent);
      border-radius: 2px;
      margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .grid-4 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .nav-dots { display: none; }
      .slide { padding: 2rem 1.25rem; }
      .hero-flex { flex-direction: column !important; }
      .mockup-phone { width: 200px; height: 400px; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .grid-4 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .top-bar-links { display: none; }
    }

    .fade-up {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(24px);
      transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease;
    }
    .fade-up.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="top-bar">
  <div class="top-bar-brand">
    <img src="/icons/logo.png" alt="مفاصل">
    <span>مفاصل <span class="accent">Mafasel</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="top-bar-links">
    <a href="/dashboard">الرئيسية</a>
    <a href="/login" class="cta"><i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> دخول</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="nav-dots" id="navDots"></div>

<!-- ══════════ SLIDE 1: COVER ══════════ -->
<section class="slide" id="s1">
  <div class="bg-glow" style="width:500px;height:500px;background:var(--accent);top:-100px;right:-100px;"></div>
  <div class="bg-glow" style="width:400px;height:400px;background:var(--purple);bottom:-80px;left:-80px;"></div>
  <div class="slide-num">01 / 12</div>
  <div class="slide-inner" style="text-align:center;">
    <div class="fade-up">
      <img src="/icons/logo.png" alt="مفاصل" style="width:90px;height:90px;margin-bottom:1.5rem;filter:drop-shadow(0 8px 32px rgba(18,169,155,0.3));">
      <h1 style="font-size:clamp(2.5rem,6vw,4rem);">
        <span class="accent">مفاصل</span>
        <br>
        <span style="font-size:0.6em;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-muted);">منصة طبية رقمية متكاملة</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="subtitle" style="margin:0 auto 2rem;max-width:600px;">
        نُعيد تعريف تجربة الرعاية الصحية الرقمية في المملكة العربية السعودية — من الاستشارة إلى التوصيل، من التأمين إلى الذكاء الاصطناعي.
      </p>
      <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <span class="badge badge-accent"><i class="fas fa-heartbeat"></i> رعاية صحية رقمية</span>
        <span class="badge badge-blue"><i class="fas fa-robot"></i> ذكاء اصطناعي</span>
        <span class="badge badge-purple"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> حماية وأمان</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════ SLIDE 2: BRAND IDENTITY ══════════ -->
<section class="slide" id="s2">
  <div class="bg-glow" style="width:450px;height:450px;background:var(--accent);bottom:-80px;right:10%;"></div>
  <div class="slide-num">02 / 12</div>
  <div class="slide-inner fade-up">
    <span class="badge badge-gold"><i class="fas fa-palette"></i> الهوية البصرية</span>
    <h2>براند <span class="gold">مفاصل</span></h2>
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
    <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
      <div>
        <p class="subtitle" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
          اسم "مفاصل" مستوحى من المفاصل في الجسم — النقاط التي تربط الأجزاء وتمنح الحركة. كذلك منصتنا تربط المرضى بالأطباء والصيدليات وشركات التأمين في نظام واحد متصل.
        </p>
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem;">
          <div class="card" style="text-align:center;">
            <div style="width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:12px;background:#101d23;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
              <div style="width:30px;height:30px;background:var(--primary);border-radius:6px;"></div>
            </div>
            <h3 style="font-size:0.82rem;">اللون الأساسي</h3>
            <code style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--text-muted);">#101d23</code>
            <p style="font-size:0.78rem;">داكن أنيق — يُعبّر عن الاحترافية والثقة الطبية</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="text-align:center;">
            <div style="width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--accent);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
              <i class="fas fa-tint" style="color:#fff;font-size:1.2rem;"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 style="font-size:0.82rem;">اللون المميّز</h3>
            <code style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--text-muted);">#12a99b</code>
            <p style="font-size:0.78rem;">تيل طبي — يوحي بالصحة والنقاء والتجدد</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="text-align:center;">
            <div style="width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(18,169,155,0.1);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
              <span style="font-family:'Tajawal';font-weight:900;font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--accent);">ت</span>
            </div>
            <h3 style="font-size:0.82rem;">الخط</h3>
            <code style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--text-muted);">Tajawal</code>
            <p style="font-size:0.78rem;">خط عربي عصري يدعم جميع الأوزان</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="text-align:center;">
            <div style="width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(139,92,246,0.1);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
              <i class="fas fa-arrow-right" style="color:var(--purple);font-size:1rem;transform:scaleX(-1);"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 style="font-size:0.82rem;">الاتجاه</h3>
            <code style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--text-muted);">RTL</code>
            <p style="font-size:0.78rem;">تصميم كامل من اليمين لليسار</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;">
        <div style="position:relative;">
          <div style="width:220px;height:220px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(18,169,155,0.2),rgba(139,92,246,0.1));display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border:2px solid rgba(18,169,155,0.2);">
            <img src="/icons/logo.png" alt="مفاصل" style="width:120px;height:120px;filter:drop-shadow(0 10px 40px rgba(18,169,155,0.4));">
          </div>
          <div style="position:absolute;top:-10px;right:-30px;background:rgba(245,197,66,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(245,197,66,0.2);border-radius:10px;padding:0.4rem 0.8rem;font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold);">
            <i class="fas fa-gem"></i> Premium
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════ SLIDE 3: VISION & MISSION ══════════ -->
<section class="slide" id="s3">
  <div class="bg-glow" style="width:400px;height:400px;background:var(--blue);top:10%;left:-100px;"></div>
  <div class="slide-num">03 / 12</div>
  <div class="slide-inner fade-up">
    <span class="badge badge-blue"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> الرؤية والرسالة</span>
    <h2>نحو مستقبل <span class="blue">صحي رقمي</span></h2>
    <div class="divider-line" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--blue),transparent);"></div>
    <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
      <div class="card" style="border-color:rgba(59,130,246,0.15);">
        <div class="card-icon" style="background:rgba(59,130,246,0.12);color:var(--blue);"><i class="fas fa-eye"></i></div>
        <h3>الرؤية</h3>
        <p>أن نكون المنصة الطبية الرقمية الرائدة في المملكة العربية السعودية والشرق الأوسط — تُحدث تحولاً حقيقياً في كيفية وصول المرضى للرعاية الصحية، بما يتماشى مع أهداف رؤية 2030 في التحول الرقمي الصحي.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="border-color:rgba(18,169,155,0.15);">
        <div class="card-icon" style="background:rgba(18,169,155,0.12);color:var(--accent);"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i></div>
        <h3>الرسالة</h3>
        <p>تقديم منصة صحية شاملة تجمع بين الاستشارات الطبية المتخصصة، الصيدلية الإلكترونية، إدارة التأمين الصحي، والذكاء الاصطناعي — في تجربة واحدة سلسة وآمنة تُبسّط الرعاية الصحية للجميع.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
      <div class="card" style="text-align:center;padding:1.25rem;">
        <div class="stat-big-num accent">10+</div>
        <div class="stat-big-label">خدمات رقمية متكاملة</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="text-align:center;padding:1.25rem;">
        <div class="stat-big-num blue">24/7</div>
        <div class="stat-big-label">دعم فني ومساعد ذكي</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="text-align:center;padding:1.25rem;">
        <div class="stat-big-num purple">100%</div>
        <div class="stat-big-label">عربي وآمن</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════ SLIDE 4: PROBLEM & SOLUTION ══════════ -->
<section class="slide" id="s4">
  <div class="bg-glow" style="width:350px;height:350px;background:var(--red);top:20%;right:-80px;"></div>
  <div class="slide-num">04 / 12</div>
  <div class="slide-inner fade-up">
    <span class="badge badge-red"><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> المشكلة والحل</span>
    <h2>لماذا <span style="color:var(--red);">نحتاج</span> مفاصل؟</h2>
    <div class="divider-line" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--red),transparent);"></div>
    <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
      <div>
        <h3 style="color:var(--red);margin-bottom:1rem;"><i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i> المشكلة</h3>
